Welcome to OHI+

You are here because you would like to plan an ocean health assessment for your area.

This platform will allow you to create and use an ocean health index as a decision-support tool for ecosystem monitoring. By the end of your assessment, you will have established a baseline estimate of how well your areas are managing ocean haelth, and meeting or exceeding, or under-perofrming in certain indicators.

